external_knowledge:
- 'Wind-sensitive sensors' refers to sensors measuring 'PeakWindSpeed';
- 'Significant amount of time' implies a duration longer than 90 days since the last maintenance;
- 'Still up and running' indicates that the sensors are currently in an 'active' status.

sql:
SELECT timestamp, sensor_id, property, value, unit 
FROM sensor_data
WHERE value > (SELECT AVG(value) FROM sensor_data);
